{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Prohibit single-sex schools",
        "additional_details": "We believe single-sex schools are bad to be in because students don't get experience of interacting with people of the opposite sex. This can hinder people in later life. Separating genders in school should not be allowed.",
        "background": "The Government should amend legislation that allows schools to have admissions policies that discriminate on the basis of sex, to prohibit single-sex schools. There should be a six month transition period, and this should apply to all years.",
